kes on Politicians’ Efforts to Ban Abortion Amid Covid-19 Outbreak</h4></a></div><div class="RelatedPosts-promo" data-reactid="255"><a href="https://theintercept.com/2020/03/30/coronavirus-ice-detention/" data-reactid="256"><div class="RelatedPosts-promo-link-thumbnail" data-reactid="257"><img height="440" src="https://theintercept-static.imgix.net/usq/eee049bc-ec6e-4c94-8a44-5e359a639349/eee049bc-ec6e-4c94-8a44-5e359a639349.bin?auto=compress,format&amp;cs=srgb&amp;dpr=2&amp;h=440&amp;w=440&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=faces%2Cedges&amp;_=784bb32b04f13f92efb1d346be5ce120" width="440" data-reactid="258"/></div><h4 class="RelatedPosts-promo-link-title" data-reactid="259">Women in ICE Detention, Fearing Coronavirus, Make Video to Protest Unsafe Conditions</h4></a></div></div><div class="Post-latest-articles" data-reactid="260"><h4 class="Post-latest-articles-header" data-reactid="261">Latest Stories</h4><div class="Promo-container" data-reactid="262"><div data-reactid="263"></div><div class="Promo Promo--default Promo--video" data-reactid="264"><a class="Promo-link" href="/2020/04/20/mehdi-hasan-arundhati-roy-live-modi-coronavirus/" data-reactid="265"><div class="GridRow" data-reactid="266"><div class="Promo-image-container" data-reactid="267"><div class="Promo-image-block" data-reactid="268"><div class="ResponsiveImage Promo-image" style="padding-top:50%;" data-reactid="269"><noscript data-reactid="270"><img src="https://theintercept-static.imgix.net/usq/d03e2be0-2ed2-4414-b5ed-aa0dc4984527/d03e2be0-2ed2-4414-b5ed-aa0dc4984527.bin?auto=compress,format&cs=srgb&dpr=2&h=450&w=900&fit=crop&crop=faces%2Cedges&_=71a8e4a6fbae9f1465366e94c2fedb44" alt="null" class="ResponsiveImage-image" height="900" width="1800"></noscript></div></div></div><div class="Promo-text" data-reactid="271"><div class="PromoVideoPlayButton Promo-playButton Promo-playButton--in-title" data-reactid="272"></div><div class="Promo-title-block" data-reactid="273"><h4 class="Promo-title" data-reactid="274"><span 